 If both players continue to choose B for the second round, they will again receive a payoff of 40$ each. This pattern of choosing B and receiving 40$ in each subsequent round would continue as long as both players maintain their initial choice.

In this game, by consistently choosing B, I can guarantee myself a steady income of 40$ per round. This strategy allows me to meet my preference for security and certainty, as the payoff is consistent and predictable.

